		dev-python/dbus-python )
	telepathy? (
		dev-python/telepathy-python
		dev-python/dbus-python
		dev-python/pygobject )
	xchat? ( net-irc/xchat-gnome )
	rhythmbox? ( media-sound/rhythmbox[zeitgeist] )
	totem? ( media-video/totem[zeitgeist] )"
